betterquesting:10.desc:8: Congratulations on passing your entrance exams, Hunter! You are now a member of an elite guild of hunters, trackers, and fighters: the Bounty Hunter's Guild. In the package accompanying this letter is some starter gear. Why don't you try it on?

§fNow that you've tried on your gear, lets get you informed of the basics of the Guild. The guild has a total of five disciplines: the §6rogues§f, most comfortable in the desert biomes; the §7knights§f, most comfortable in the forests and plains; the §9§arangers§f, most comfortable in the swamps and jungles; the §b§9duelists§f, most comfortable in the oceans; and the §bberserkers§f, most comfortable in the frozen biomes. Each discipline has its own unique set of weapons and armor, though all can be mastered in time. Leveling up a discipline requires you to slay mobs endemic to your chosen region, and each level you unlock will attract stronger and stronger mobs in each region.

Now that you understand the basic existance of disciplines, it is time for you to choose which discipline you would like to start out with. Take some food while you're at it, its hard to think on an empty stomach.
